title: Embroidered skirt
description: Calf-length, fitted skirt in woven fabric made from a viscose blend with embroidery in a contrasting colour. Wrapover front and a high waist with a button. Unlined.

title: Crochet-look dress
description: Calf-length, fitted, sleeveless dress in a textured knit with a crocheted look. Narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and a V-neckline with a keyhole opening at the front. Gently frilled hem.

title: Cropped halterneck top
description: Cropped, fitted halterneck top in woven fabric. Crossover straps with buttons at the back of the neck and wide ties that fasten at the back. Lined at the front.

title: Cropped crochet-look vest top
description: Cropped, fitted vest top in a textured knit with a crocheted look. Deep, square neckline at the front and back, and a narrow trim around the neckline and armholes.

title: Double-breasted blazer
description: Loose-fit, double-breasted blazer in woven fabric with peak lapels and buttons at the front. Shoulder pads, long sleeves, a welt chest pocket and front pockets. Lined.

title: Linen-blend mini skirt
description: Mini skirt in a viscose and linen weave with a low waist and a concealed zip with a button at the back. Lined.

title: Crochet-look skirt
description: Calf-length, fitted skirt in a textured knit with a crocheted look. High waist with covered elastication, and long fringes at the hem.

title: Padded platform sandals
description: Rose Gold Plated Double Flared Tunnel Plug Earrings. Made of 316L Stainless SteelPlatform sandals in a weave with wide, padded crossover foot straps. Patterned soles.

title: Crinkled jersey dress
description: Calf-length, fitted dress in crinkled jersey in a sleeveless design with narrow, adjustable shoulder straps.

title: Buttoned tie-belt dress
description: Ankle-length dress in a viscose blend weave with a deep V-neckline and covered buttons down the front. Long, raglan cut balloon sleeves with narrow, covered elastication at the cuffs. Tie belt at the waist and a gathered tier at the hem to add width and volume. Unlined.

title: Crochet-look lace dress
description: Ankle-length dress in lace with a crocheted look. Slightly wider, round neckline and an opening with a covered button at the back of the neck. Long sleeves and a high slit at each side of the hem. Scalloped edges at the cuffs and hem. Unlined.

title: Tailored trousers
description: Tailored trousers with a high waist, pleats at the top, a zip fly with a hook-and-eye fastening and a concealed button. Diagonal side pockets, welt back pockets and wide, straight legs with creases.

title: Braided-detail shorts
description: Shorts in a woven viscose blend. High waist with a concealed zip and hook-and-eye fastening at the back. Discreet pockets in the side seams and circular loop trims with braided ties down each side.

title: Rib-knit dress
description: Calf-length, fitted dress in a rib knit with crochet-look cups and narrow, adjustable shoulder straps.

title: Satin slip dress
description: Calf-length, fitted dress in softly draping viscose satin with a V-shaped neckline, adjustable spaghetti shoulder straps and shaped cups. Concealed zip and hook-and-eye fastener at the back and a straight-cut hem.

title: Flared trousers
description: Trousers in woven fabric made from a viscose blend with a zip fly and button, diagonal side pockets and legs with gently flared hems.

title: Jacquard-weave shopper
description: Shopper in a cotton blend jacquard weave with decorative straps at the short sides and long handles at the top. Open inner compartment. Lined. Depth 20 cm. Height 31 cm. Width 38 cm.

title: Linen shorts
description: Shorts in airy linen with a regular waist that has covered elastication and a small frill at the top. Diagonal side pockets.

title: Linen shorts
description: Shorts in airy linen with a regular waist that has covered elastication and a small frill at the top. Diagonal side pockets.

title: T-shirt Cream/Atelier 93
description: T-shirt in soft jersey with a rib-trimmed neckline.
